OL,3,CEnergy bill rise: Elderly couple ask
OL,4,Cdo we eat or heat?
OL,6,FA couple from Hailsham, Sussex say
OL,7,Fthey'll have to choose between heating
OL,8,For eating this winter with the cost of
OL,9,Fenergy rising by 10 per cent from
OL,10,Ftoday (1 October).
OL,12,FDavid and Naomi Younge are among 10
OL,13,Fmillion pensioners who will lose out
OL,14,Fon financial support from the
OL,15,FGovernment because the winter fuel
OL,16,Fpayment is now being means tested.
OL,18,FNaomi is disabled with limited
OL,19,Fmobility and feels the cold more so
OL,20,Faffording heating is vital.
