OL,3,CEnergy bill rise: Elderly couple ask
OL,4,Cdo we eat or heat?
OL,6,FDavid added: "A country is judged on
OL,7,Fhow it looks after its elderly people.
OL,8,FAt the moment, at the time of
OL,9,Fspeaking, this country is judged as
OL,10,Frubbish because it's not looking after
OL,11,Fits elderly people and I think that is
OL,12,Fa shocking indictment of one of the
OL,13,Ffinest countries in the world."
OL,15,FThe average household energy bill will
OL,16,Fincrease by #149 a year from Tuesday
OL,17,Fas Ofgem increases its price cap, just
OL,18,Fas homes move into the winter months.
