OL,3,CEnergy bill rise: Elderly couple ask
OL,4,Cdo we eat or heat?
OL,6,FThe regulator has raised the cap from
OL,7,Fthe current #1,568 for a typical dual
OL,8,Ffuel household in England, Scotland
OL,9,Fand Wales to #1,717, or around #12 a
OL,10,Fmonth more on an average bills.
OL,12,FWith the rising prices, households
OL,13,Fhave also been advised to see whether
OL,14,Fnow is the time to change their energy
OL,15,Ftariff, to beat the October price
OL,16,Fhikes.
