OL,6,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,7,FBrearley urged consumers to "shop
OL,8,Faround" and consider a fixed-rate
OL,9,Ftariff that could save money, adding
OL,10,Fthat the regulator was working with
OL,11,FGovernment, suppliers, charities and
OL,12,Fconsumer groups to do "everything we
OL,13,Fcan" to support customers.
