OL,3,CEnergy bill rise: Elderly couple ask
OL,4,Cdo we eat or heat?
OL,6,FUswitch energy spokesman, Ben
OL,7,FGallizzi, added: "There are a number
OL,8,Fof fixed tariffs worth considering
OL,9,Fright now. By opting for a fixed deal,
OL,10,Fyou're locking in those rates for the
OL,11,Fduration ` usually 12 months ` which
OL,12,Fmeans households could have price
OL,13,Fcertainty and avoid the ups and downs
OL,14,Fof the price cap."
OL,16,FThe price cap sets a maximum price
OL,17,Fthat energy suppliers can charge
OL,18,Fconsumers for each kilowatt hour (kWh)
OL,19,Fof energy they use.
